Required software/libraries:

* Subversion/dynamag access:
install seahorse, make keypair for dynamag login
simlink /var/www/user
sftp access to sim, home: add entry to "places" in dolphin
install kdesvn

* CUDA
cuda 3.0 + devdriver
compute-exclusive mode?
export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/cuda/bin
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/usr/local/cuda/lib64:/usr/local/cuda/lib
export C_INCLUDE_PATH=$C_INCLUDE_PATH:/usr/local/cuda/include
export CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH=$CPLUS_INCLUDE_PATH:/usr/local/cuda/include

* Go
export GOROOT=$HOME/sbin/go
export GOOS=linux
export GOARCH=amd64
export GOBIN=$HOME/sbin
sudo cp sbin/go/misc/kate/go.xml /usr/share/kde4/apps/katepart/syntax/

* env. variables:
edit .bashrc
export PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/cuda/bin:/home/XXX/YYY/trunk/bin
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=$LD_LIBRARY_PATH:/usr/local/cuda/lib64:/usr/local/cuda/lib

* Compiling FFTW:
./configure CFLAGS="-fPIC" --enable-float  --enable-threads --enable-sse
make
sudo make install

* Dependencies for scripts etc:
ffmpeg gnuplot


(* general Ubuntu)
sudo apt-get install build-essential ubuntu-restricted-extras flashplugin
automount win partition:
/etc/fstab:  /dev/sdaXXX /media/xp ntfs-3g defaults,locale=en_US.utf8 0 0
ln -s /media/xp /home/XXX/My\ Documents


